title: Evil In Law - Season 1
description:
Evil In Law - Season 1

EVIL IN-LAW reveals great marriages nearly ruined when a maniacal, meddling mother-in-law overstepped her bounds. They are stories that make you want to elope: the mother who slowly poisoned her daughter-in-law so she could raise the grandchildren as her own; the mother who tried to seduce her son-in-law because she was jealous of her own daughter; or the mother who faked a fatal illness to get her son to turn on his wife and move back in with mommy.

Ep 1 - Mama's Boy
Ep 2 - Hidden Evil
Ep 3 - Dying For Love
Ep 4 - Heaven Turns To Hell
Ep 5 - Love, Greed & Murder
Ep 6 - Fatal Obsession
Ep 7 - Love's Fury
